---
description: Git and commit conventions — Conventional Commits, branch naming
globs: **/.git/**, **/*.ts, **/*.tsx
alwaysApply: false
---
Commit messages must follow Conventional Commits:
  feat|fix|refactor|chore|docs|test|style: short description
Never commit directly to main — always branch.
Branch names: feature/*, fix/*, refactor/*, chore/*.
Every feature must include at minimum one unit test.
